..TEXT:
|e giuso, intra ' mortali~: This turn of phrase,
balancing the ^qui~ {v.10} of Heaven, returns us to earth and
history, to a focus that will end on the figure of Dante, the
mortal man who has been uplifted to this highest of places from
that lowly world.
