..TEXT:
|speranza~: "Hope" is very much of the mortal world
and has no ^active~ place in the immortal world of the angels and
the elect, despite the fact that St. James could represent that
virtue and love it still (^Par.~ XXV, 82-84).  |vivace~:
"Inexhaustible."
