..TEXT:
|In te misericordia~... |bontate~: This third of
the three tercets specifically dedicated to the praise of Mary is
the culminating one.  Note especially vss. 20-21, where it is
said that ^all~ goodness to be found in any and all creatures is
to be found in her.  |magnificenza~: The word may be understood
as "munificence" as well as "magnificence" in the sense of "power
to achieve lofty things."
