..TEXT:
|che 'l parlar mostra~: Some editors have accepted
the reading "che 'l parlar nostro," but Petrocchi's acceptance of
|mostra~ seems justifiable (see his note on this).  The theme is
not only that of memory's shortcoming, but of the inability even
to convey that which is remembered.  Thus the poet's struggle is
a double one, to remember and to express, each of these efforts
falling short of full attainment, as subsequent verses now
repeatedly affirm.
