..TEXT:
|E' mi ricorda~: The impersonal use of the verb, now
with the impersonal subject expressed, |e'~ ("it") -- literally,
"it remembers me."  |ardito~: "Bold" (but in a good sense).  The
adjective serves to keep to the fore the wayfarer's active
participation in the final movement toward final vision, which is
now declared.
