..TEXT:
|legato con amore in un volume~: For the familiar
metaphor of the book of the created universe, see C. S. Singleton
(1949), pp. 37-41.  This book is now seen to be contained in the
Godhead and there bound by love.
..TCHR:
210
..AUTH:
