..TEXT:
|sembiante~: "Appearance," but with the suggestion
of "face," and therefore already the suggestion of person, of a
personal God.  This is merely a suggestion, of course, for a face
as such is not actually beheld here (unless in our human image
within the Second Person), but such is not the meaning.
