..TEXT:
|ma per la vista~... |si travagliava~: The
wayfarer's powers of vision increase momentarily, as ^he~ changes
(it being unthinkable that the object of his vision should
change).  The verb |travagliare~ suggests, however, the
^struggle~ on the part of the wayfarer toward clearer and clearer
vision (cf. the English ^travail~).
