|Oh quanto~... |"poco"~: Again the poet's voice
conveying the familiar theme of the inexpressibility of this
final experience.  |al mio concetto~: "Compared to what I
remember now," conceive now in memory.  |e questo~... |"poco"~:
And what I now remember is such (i.e., so little) that it is not
enough to say "little."  One should rather say "almost nothing."
