..TEXT:
|per misurar lo cerchio~: In ^De mon.~ III, iii,
2, Dante notes: "Geometra circuli quadraturam ignorat."  ("The
geometrician knows not how to square the circle.")  See ^Conv.~
II, xiii, 27: "Lo cerchio per lo suo arco @e impossibile a
quadrare perfettamente."  ("The circle, because of its curve, is
impossible to square perfectly.")
