..TEXT:
|tal era io~... ^s'indova~ {v.138}: The posture of
cool scrutiny continues, scrutiny of the deepest mystery of the
faith, the Incarnation.  This geometer (in metaphor) really
desires to square the circle, meaning to make out how the flesh,
our human flesh and image, can be fitted, ^is~ fitted, into the
circle of divinity.
..TCHR:
